# Spec traceability ([CFHA-VER-005])

If you edit a **SHALL** in `openspec/specs/*/spec.md`: follow **`docs/adrs/0003-spec-test-traceability.md`** for ID shapes and spec ↔ test cross-links; update **`docs/spec-test-traceability.md`** (matrix row); add bracketed IDs to pytest docstrings or helm unittest comments for listed evidence files. Run **`./ci.sh`** (includes `scripts/check_spec_traceability.py`). Occasionally re-validate rows vs evidence paths.
